scanning single target - only first important 1000 ports
nmap 127.0.0.1

scanning multiple targets
nmap 198.26.21.10 127.0.0.1

scanning an ip add range
nmap -p 1-2500 127.0.0.1

scanning all ip ports
nmap -p - 127.0.0.1

scanning udp ports
nmap -sU 127.0.0.1

scanning tcp ports
nmap -sT 127.0.0.1

tcp + udp
nmap -sT -sU -p 50-500 127.0.0.1

tcp all ports 
nmap -sT -p - 127.0.0.1

os fingerprint
nmap -O 127.0.0.1

os fingerprint with more details
nmap -O -v 127.0.0.1
